{
  "stem": "22447.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Guildford, it was-- from Guildford, a few months before the invasion, we were shifted to the London Glider Club.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Near Luton, is it?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Dunstable.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "London Glider Club.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Dunstable.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "On Dunstable Downs.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we knew-- we knew it was France because we got phrase books, how to say it in French.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we knew it was France.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then they-- they said, all the vehicles-- not the motorcycles, you couldn't take the motorcycles-- but all the lorries, had to be, what they called, waterproofed and fireproofed.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They put a clay around the plugs, and the-- and the electrical systems, and then they had another clay for waterproofing it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when you go off the landing barge, you go through the-- maybe, a few yards of water.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it shouldn't affect the engine, and the exhausts were shifted around.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Instead of being under the vehicle, they were shifted around and they went up the sides of the vehicle, out just past the roof.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the exhaust was actually-- and if you look at today, at the-- at the big lorries, they've got the exhaust going up.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not the long side, but they go up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So-- what-- and one was to seal the petrol tanks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But once the petrol tanks were sealed, we knew you couldn't-- there's only one place you can go.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Down to the docks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was on a Sunday, and we worked it out then the D-Day must be on the Tuesday.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because by the time you get down to the docks, and you can only go one way, you can't fill up anymore.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But something happened in the War Office.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They actually started the invasion, and something happened, it was canceled.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they put it back 24 hours.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
